# MiniLinearTransformation.Core.Laws

Axioms and laws governing linear transformations.
-/

import MiniLinearTransformation.Core.Basic
import MiniLinearTransformation.Core.Objects

namespace MiniLinearTransformation

open MiniVectorSpaceCore

/-!
## Laws of Linear Transformations

1. Linearity: T(x + y) = T(x) + T(y)
2. Scalar multiplication: T(a·x) = a·T(x)
3. Composition is associative
4. Identity is neutral for composition
-/

end MiniLinearTransformation
